Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙海盗哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老样子 又要继续旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是自己选的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是希望偶尔有美女包围我这样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天无聊的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭是我现在最大的享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂 又是营养套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦放松机能就会变得迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想要在酒池肉林和美女游玩变成呆子的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放烟花吗？还真华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是慧星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有情调
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧星在玩捉迷藏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四话 魔王加鲁丹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎参加我的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 让我躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个邪恶的男人在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里！包你安心啦 可爱小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙还真够大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拉美，我知道你躲在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要回去你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我选的话 我比较喜欢这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想惹我生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够缠人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然要你吃点苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我吃苦头？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满口大话的小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶你这个大头鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会你可别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用电磁护壁教训你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样嘛 和我一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少来了，大头鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问也不问屋主 就擅自跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被揍就快滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛？叫我离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道痛了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次有人能打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也第一次有人反抗我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子！我要把你撕成两半！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂，顺便为这位客人准备份晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮有一手的！小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找这种有骨气的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你做我的仆人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏被我遇见这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫比拉美吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王加鲁丹的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王加鲁丹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个大头鬼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁丹是个可怕的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也从加鲁丹那里学得一点魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想利用这力量从逃出这里…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 为了我害你遇上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里！这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这些了，你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁丹想要你做他的仆人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样欢迎未来的仆人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你继续留在这里的话，就被他用魔法控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要我逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的拍档瑞蒂和船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的船和机械人都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被冻结在时之房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻结？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法来停止住时间的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管的话，他们就会变成石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先带我到那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太令人吃惊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些财宝是魔王加鲁丹从各个星球的人手中抢来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是这宝石 加鲁丹靠他可以自由伸缩的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和魔法的力量 夺取各星球的女人与人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才逼着要我当他的仆人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么点本事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 飞稳一点要不然我会晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我只会一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么无证驾驶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开闪开闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来地方看来不怎么妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和这个男人说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫哥普拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 喜欢这艘船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是泰拉斯星的国王也没有机会住这么美丽的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女要多少就有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在寻找你这种勇敢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你看得起我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样要不要和我一起去进攻各个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金银珠宝和大把的软妹子，想要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说不呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想惹我生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌受人驱使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还没有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是请求 是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不留情了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你吞下的是气球种子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气球种子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的每个人都吞下过气球种子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有人敢反抗我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 别用那种眼光看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是开玩笑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？要当我的仆人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不当你的仆人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把嘴巴张开！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你来拿出气球种子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅！比拉美！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出来了 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢忤逆我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不听话的小家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要把你变成气球然后撑爆它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然也会那个魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加鲁丹教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趁现在逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭娘们 竟敢戏弄我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是时之房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的船和同伴被冻结在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 明明没有人却感觉有很多眼光注视我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动！你看！石像在动！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是普通的石像！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被加鲁丹用魔法变成石像的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是人偶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…我的船！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的变成石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拉美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是魔法方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能想想办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法或咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不打倒加鲁丹，魔法就没有办法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个家伙是个怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间的某处藏有骷髅头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射穿那个骷髅头的眉间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉间？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是加鲁丹作梦时自己说的，他唯一的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个房间里德骷髅头？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都没看到骷髅头！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找过好几次也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁丹的梦话可信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 一定藏在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拉美！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退后！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没叫你来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试几次才能死心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少装个疼痛的样子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？知道我的厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿不愿意做我的仆人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真够缠人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是难对付的汽车推销员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到…这就是大魔王的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命！放我出去！求求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉 哥普拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么我都愿意做！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经在这里被封印了三千年了，好不容易出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个贪心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面再呆个三千年吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的美女！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们要我来做国王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被美女包围的桃源乡又消失在梦中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正海盗哥普拉的命运就是如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远方星星来 ，到远方的星星去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8年前因格星的贝根救过我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在他变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一点希望我都投入极大的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因格星的标志物龙水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它从基尔顿那里抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给予帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遇上麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了巨大的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集\N龙水晶的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见面吧

